;資料表示の目次

@REFERENCE_ENTRANCE

CLEARLINE LINECOUNT
PRINTL This is a reference room where you can find information about the world of this game.
PRINTL Please note that this is basically useless for gameplay.
PRINTL Also note that the setting can be subject to change at your convenience.
DRAWLINE
PRINTL [ 0] Shelf on Worldview
PRINTL [ 1] Shelf on Races
PRINTL [ 2] Shelf on Makai's Residents
DRAWLINE
PRINTL [ 9] Return to Title
INPUT

SELECTCASE RESULT
CASE 0
	CALL REFERENCE_WORLD
	
CASE 1
	CALL REFERENCE_TRIBE
	
CASE 2
	CALL REFERENCE_RESIDENTS

CASE 9
	RETURN
	
ENDSELECT
RESTART


